title: SPY Presents: Behind The Scenes w/ Alana Blanchard + The Fiona
description: SPY® and photographer Chris Straley made their way out to the North Shore for a photo shoot with Kauai girl and surf industry bombshell Alana Blanchard. Check out this short-but-sweet behind look into how it all went down.
